# <%= @current_superagent.superagent_type.titleize %>: <%= @current_superagent.name %>

<% if !@current_superagent.is_main_superagent? && @current_user && @current_heartbeat.nil? -%>
## Heartbeat Required

You must send a heartbeat to access this <%= @current_superagent.superagent_type %> for the current cycle.

## [Actions](<%= @current_superagent.path %>/actions)

* [`send_heartbeat()`](<%= @current_superagent.path %>/actions/send_heartbeat) - Send a heartbeat to confirm your presence
<% elsif @current_user && !@is_viewing_current_cycle && @current_heartbeat.nil? -%>
## Heartbeat Required

You must send a heartbeat to view past cycles.

## [Actions](<%= @current_superagent.path %>/actions)

* [`send_heartbeat()`](<%= @current_superagent.path %>/actions/send_heartbeat) - Send a heartbeat to confirm your presence
<% else -%>
## Cycle: <%= @cycle.name.titleize %>

<% unless @is_viewing_current_cycle -%>
Viewing: <%= @cycle.name.titleize %> | [Back to current cycle](<%= @current_superagent.path %>)
<% end -%>

## Activity Feed

<% if @feed_items.empty? -%>
No activity in this cycle yet.
<% else -%>
<% @feed_items.first(20).each do |feed_item| -%>
* **<%= feed_item[:type] %>**: [<%= raw feed_item[:item].title %>](<%= feed_item[:item].path %>) by <%= user_link_md(feed_item[:created_by]) %> (<%= time_ago_in_words(feed_item[:created_at]) %> ago)
<% end -%>
<% end -%>

## Explore

* [Cycles](<%= @current_superagent.path %>/cycles)
* [Backlinks](<%= @current_superagent.path %>/backlinks)

## Pinned

<% if @pinned_items.any? -%>
<% @pinned_items.each do |item| -%>
* <%= item[:item].class.to_s %>: [<%= raw item[:item].title %>](<%= item[:item].path %>) pinned <%= time_ago_in_words(item[:pinned_at]) %> ago
<% end -%>
<% else -%>
No pinned items yet.
<% end -%>

## Team

<% if @team.any? -%>
<% @team.each do |user| -%>
* <%= user_link_md(user) %>
<% end -%>
<% else -%>
No team members yet.
<% end -%>

## [Actions](<%= @current_superagent.path %>/actions)

* [New Note](<%= @current_superagent.path %>/note)
